Method Detail

readingStarted

void readingStarted()
Called when NMEA data is found in stream and reader starts dispatching SentenceEvents. Also, this notification occurs when events dispatching continues after readingStopped() has occurred.

readingStopped

void readingStopped()
Called when SentenceReader has not received any new data within last 5 seconds.

sentenceRead

void sentenceRead(SentenceEvent event)
Invoked when a valid NMEA 0183 sentence has been read.

Parameters:
event - SentenceEvent to dispatch
